joseph marshall walker july 1 , 1784 -- january 20 , 1856 louisiana soldier politician . 
13th governor louisiana , . 
walker bear english father mother french quarter new orleans , louisiana . 
time louisiana colony spain . 
1807 , go mexico join spanish army , serve lieutenant dragoon , later become master military school chihuahua . 
